Here are some command line codes to use the features of this Raspberry Pi:


Capture Picture:
raspistill -o {file name}.jpg
Example:
raspistill -o tilapiacam1.jpg


Capture Video:
raspivid -o {file name).h264 -t {time in ms}
Example:
raspivid -o tilapiacam2.h264 -t 10000


View Pictures:
Navigate to where the picture has been saved (for example: /home/pi)
Double click on the image

Replay video:
omxplayer /{file path}/{file name}
Example:
omxplayer /home/pi/video.h264


